T02D3520:165b-5: dang po snying gar zla ba la tsum yig dkar po'i sa bon bltas la /
T02D3520:165b-6: de'i 'od zer gyis sangs rgyas la sogs pa rnams la mchod pa dang /
T02D3520:165b-8: yang dag par bstod pa dang /
T02D3520:165b-9: sdig pa bshags pa la sogs pa bla na med
T02D3520:165b-10: pa'i mchod pa rnam pa bdun gyis mchod pa'i rjes
T02D3520:165b-11: la gsum la skyabs su 'gro ba'i tshigs su bcad
T02D3520:165b-12: pa brjod nas bzod par gsol te /
T02D3520:165b-13: tshad med pa'i gnas bzhi rnam par bsgom zhing stong pa nyid bsam par bya'o //
T02D3520:165b-14: de nas sna tshogs padma dang zla ba la yang
T02D3520:165b-15: rang gi sa bon bsam zhing de yongs su gyur
T02D3520:165b-16: pa las 'phags ma tsunde ston ka'i zla ba lta
T02D3520:165b-17: bu zhal gcig phyag bzhi pa /
T02D3520:165b-19: phyag g-yon pa pu stis mtshan pa'i padma ;
T02D3520:165b-20: phyag lhag ma dag gis lhung bzed bsnams pa /
T02D3520:165b-21: rgyan dang na bza' sna tshogs pas rnam par brgyan pa rdo rje sems dpa'i cod pan can /
T02D3520:165b-22: sems can dpag tu med pa'i don mdzad pa'i sku'i
T02D3520:165b-23: bdag nyid spro zhing skad cig gis bskyed nas rang
T02D3520:165b-24: gi sa bon snying gar bsams te phyag rgya gnas
T02D3520:165b-26: lag pa gnyis thal mo sbyar nas mdzub mo gnyis
T02D3520:165b-27: gung mo'i dkyil du 'khyil pa'i rnam par sbyar te
T02D3520:165b-28: / mtheb chen gnyis logs su sbyar ba'o //
T02D3520:165b-30: aom tsa le tsu le tsunde sv'a h'a /
